						Pinterest
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			
			<!-- Thank You Section -->
			<div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 text-center">
				<p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
					Thank you for visiting the National Park Directory. We hope our resources help you plan your next adventure in the great outdoors!
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
